                    <span>First of all, the book is great.  However, the workshop exercises have to be downloaded from Kevins site.  Even that wouldn't be so bad if they weren't compressed by some funky program called StuffIt.  StuffIt has to be downloaded as well and installed on the PC.  Every hear of ZIP!</span>
                  
              
